Castle Types:

Each outdoor square can house 5x5 inner rooms. One room is taken up
along the outside walls for wall. You must have courtyard rooms to make
a stable or larege barracks.

      Outdoor     Indoors
Size  Squares  Courtyard/Keep  Stables  Barracks      Towers    Influence
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1        1         0/4x4        N/A     1 small       5 sm         5
 2        4       9x9/4x4         1     1 sm,1 lg   4 sm, 1 lg      6
 3        9     14x14/7x7         2     1 sm,2 lg   8 sm, 5 lg      7
 4       16     19x19/10x10       3     2 sm,3 lg   12sm, 6 lg      8
 5       25     24x24/13x13       4     3 sm,4 lg   16sm, 13lg      9

1) 1 small tower at each corner, 1 small tower on keep.
2) 1 small tower at each corner, 1 large on keep.
3) 1 small/large tower at each corner, 1 small at each mid-wall, 
   1 large on keep.
4) 1 small/large tower at each corner, 2 small on each wall,
   2 large on keep.
5) 1 small/large tower at each corner, 2 small on each wall,
   1 small/large tower at mid-wall, 4 large towers on keep

Small towers are 1 indoor room in size. Large towers are 4 (2x2).

